// Triết standard library — std.collections
//
// Generic collection types: `Vector<T>`, `HashMap<K, V>`. Backed by
// VM builtins shipped in v0.7.3 + exposed via path_to_builtin
// resolution per ADR-0019 Addendum §A7.
//
// Java-aesthetic: each container lives in its own sub-module, mirror
// `java.util.{Vector, HashMap}`.
module vector
module hashmap
